message.body: So have u ever won anything thru the Penn State studies?
(1/2)Hey..! No, I didn't really win anything at Penn. All I got was a good GPA and a couple of research papers. :P I participated in a couple of sports
(2/2)tournaments, but we just weren't good enough. How'd your weekend go?
I meant have you won anything as a result of your participation in this Penn State discussion panel
I went to a Dbacks ball game Fri night, then rode my bike and worked both Sat & Sun. Nothing too exciting but a fine weekend...you?
(1/2)Oh, no. Not yet, anyway. It's going to be a draw *if* we qualify. My weekend was bad :( Had to work long hours to meet a deadline. Went home at 11:30 pm on
(2/2)a Sunday night, so that should tell you everything. Say, what kind of parties do you DJ?
That blows! I hope they compensate u well.:-)
I DJ any kind of event. Most common ones are: weddings, bday parties, holiday parties (Christmas & New Years, Halloween), daddy/daughter dances, kids' po
